{
  "id": "69d39308da764e564709dae9",
  "title": "2026-04-07~10 Mijikko",
  "created": 1775473417,
  "updated": 1775550911,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d39308da764e564709dae9",
      "text": "2026-04-07~10 Mijikko",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473417,
      "updated": 1775473429
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393080000000000caa238",
      "text": "[2026-04-04~06 Mijikko] -> 2026-04-07~10 Mijikko -> [2026-04-Next Mijikko]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473417,
      "updated": 1775473513
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3cb980000000000e8929f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775487897,
      "updated": 1775487897
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3cb980000000000e892a0",
      "text": "[[共通]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775487897,
      "updated": 1775487900
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393080000000000caa239",
      "text": " やはりページ作成がめんどくさいので、金曜日までの日記を全部予め作成しておいた[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473417,
      "updated": 1775487904
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3cb750000000000e8929d",
      "text": " \t多分平日４日間程度なので、そんなに長くならない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775487861,
      "updated": 1775487904
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3cb910000000000e8929e",
      "text": " \t長くなったら別途切り出せば良い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775487890,
      "updated": 1775487904
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3cb5d0000000000e8929b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775487838,
      "updated": 1775487838
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393080000000000caa23a",
      "text": "[[日記 [2026-04-07]]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473417,
      "updated": 1775473472
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3931a0000000000caa262",
      "text": "\t夜中だけどもうちょっと作業するのだ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473434,
      "updated": 1775487704
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3d29700000000001c00a1",
      "text": "\t🖤🖤🖤　普通",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775489688,
      "updated": 1775489834
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3d30f00000000001c00a2",
      "text": "\t\t🩶🖤🖤　返信が制限されてる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775489807,
      "updated": 1775489865
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3d31a00000000001c00a4",
      "text": "\t\t🩶🩶🖤　鍵がかかってる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775489819,
      "updated": 1775489859
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3d36300000000001c00a6",
      "text": "\t\t🖤🩶🖤　これも鍵",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775489892,
      "updated": 1775489899
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3d31c00000000001c00a5",
      "text": "\t\t🩶🩶🩶　ブロックされてる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775489820,
      "updated": 1775489869
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3d3f100000000001c00a7",
      "text": "\t[グラタン]って家で作る以外で食べられるとこあんまなくない？",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775490034,
      "updated": 1775490048
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3ea9b00000000001c00a8",
      "text": "\t\tコンビニや冷凍食品であるらしいので食べてみよ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775495836,
      "updated": 1775495865
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3eaa700000000001c00a9",
      "text": "\t就活タスク少し進めた",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775495848,
      "updated": 1775495853
    },
    {
      "id": "69d453f00000000000efa91b",
      "text": "\t最近の井戸端は忙しいな",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775522798,
      "updated": 1775522805
    },
    {
      "id": "69d453f70000000000efa91c",
      "text": "\t　[自分の意見にはアイコンつけて欲しい]とか",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775522805,
      "updated": 1775522825
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4540c0000000000efa91d",
      "text": "\t　[できればリンクしかないページは作らないでいただきたい]とか",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775522825,
      "updated": 1775522852
    },
    {
      "id": "69d454270000000000efa91e",
      "text": "\t　片方持ちかけたの[Mijikko.icon]だけど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775522852,
      "updated": 1775522863
    },
    {
      "id": "69d480fa0000000000f0768f",
      "text": "\tガチ眠くて泣いてる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775534331,
      "updated": 1775534335
    },
    {
      "id": "69d481000000000000f07690",
      "text": "\t　あくび泣き",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775534337,
      "updated": 1775534342
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bea000000000007c743f",
      "text": "\t　ほんまに今日は眠い、何なんだろう",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550112,
      "updated": 1775550120
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bf8b000000000084c65e",
      "text": "\t　今日眠い、同意[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1775550348,
      "updated": 1775550357
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bf9a00000000007c7446",
      "text": "\t　　これは[井戸端おふとん部]の機運…？[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550362,
      "updated": 1775550382
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4beb300000000007c7440",
      "text": "\tAをするならAされる覚悟が必要、みたいなの、一部同意だけど一部否定",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550131,
      "updated": 1775550250
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bf1000000000007c7441",
      "text": "\t　その内、気が向いたらページ作るかも（多分作らない）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550224,
      "updated": 1775550558
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bf2000000000007c7442",
      "text": "\t　同意面",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550240,
      "updated": 1775550260
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bf3600000000007c7444",
      "text": "\t　　心構えとして、自分のAを主張するなら相手のAを受け入れるというのは協調性の面で良い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550262,
      "updated": 1775550318
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bf3400000000007c7443",
      "text": "\t　否定面",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550260,
      "updated": 1775550262
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bf7100000000007c7445",
      "text": "\t　　Aを受け入れる覚悟が無い人に対してAをするのは協調性の面で悪い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550322,
      "updated": 1775550345
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4c19e0000000000443c33",
      "text": " \t　　Aを受け入れる覚悟がないけどAする人はどう？[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775550878,
      "updated": 1775550911
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bfd600000000007c7447",
      "text": "\t　ちょっとA自体をちゃんと言語化できてないので、誤解の余地出来ちゃってるかもしれないのはすみません",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550422,
      "updated": 1775550450
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bffe00000000007c7448",
      "text": "\t　　任意のAを当てはめて頂ければ良いかも",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775550462,
      "updated": 1775550473
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4bfb80000000000548fb3",
      "text": "\t\t[nyarla.icon]「AをするならAをされる覚悟が必要」と言う類いの話、極端なことを言うと、",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1775550393,
      "updated": 1775550710
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4c00f0000000000548fb4",
      "text": "\t\t\t>人を殺してもよい者は人に殺される覚悟のあるものだけだ、しかしだからと言って人を殺すことは肯定されないし、殺される覚悟がないのであれば、人を殺すべきではない",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1775550480,
      "updated": 1775550613
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4c1350000000000443c32",
      "text": "\t\t\tこれ[キノの旅]の殺人が合法的な街でほぼ同じような内容を描写してた[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775550773,
      "updated": 1775550828
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4c0140000000000548fb5",
      "text": "\t\tになりそう……？[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1775550484,
      "updated": 1775550513
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4c0330000000000548fb7",
      "text": "\t\t\t[nyarla.icon]としてはこれに類する話になるのかな、と感じてます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1775550516,
      "updated": 1775550674
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4c1060000000000548fb9",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t武士とかの覚悟の話っぽさがあるような気もする",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1775550727,
      "updated": 1775550737
    },
    {
      "id": "69d4c0a60000000000548fb8",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tとは言え例えが物騒すぎる……",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1775550630,
      "updated": 1775550740
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3caca000000000063be0a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775489826,
      "updated": 1775489826
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3932a0000000000caa263",
      "text": "[[日記 [2026-04-08]]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473450,
      "updated": 1775473476
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393350000000000caa266",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473461,
      "updated": 1775473461
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3932e0000000000caa264",
      "text": "[[日記 [2026-04-09]]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473454,
      "updated": 1775473479
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393360000000000caa267",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473462,
      "updated": 1775473462
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393310000000000caa265",
      "text": "[[日記 [2026-04-10]]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473457,
      "updated": 1775473482
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393080000000000caa25d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473417,
      "updated": 1775473417
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393080000000000caa25e",
      "text": "[[タスク]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473417,
      "updated": 1775473417
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393080000000000caa25f",
      "text": "\t就活",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775473417,
      "updated": 1775473444
    },
    {
      "id": "69d393080000000000caa261",
